Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur looked among the others. There were some that were 
damaged, even one by his own feet. The thought of him leaving them 
crossed his mind. Megatron, he heard had abandoned them. There was 
not much use. He thought this group was weak. They acted too much 
like Maximals to be real Predacons. 

He ducked his head and sqwaked lightly. 

They were weak.
